<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">将被乘数的个位数移并到乘数个位数上，使二位数乘二位数变为一位数乘二位数，再加两个乘数个位数相乘的积。可利用公式</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">[(10a+b)+c][(10a+c)-c]+bc</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算，其中a是被乘数十位上的数字，b、c分别是被乘数、乘数个位上的数字。</Run>
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">53×58=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 53×58</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=(53+8)×(58-8)+3×8</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=61×50+24</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=3050+24</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=3074</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>